<plot>Across the Atlantic traces the experiences of Dutch immigrants who came to Canada in post-World War II. Through interviews with three generations of Dutch immigrants, this film explores the motivations behind migration, the challenges faced in their first years in Canada, and the impact this migration had on their future lives and families.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?022614</url></doc>
